<normalizedToken originalValue="Sloane’s">Sloane's</normalizedToken>
illustration as 
<typeStatus>
<typeStatus>lectotype</typeStatus>
</typeStatus>
, with 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Sloane’s">Sloane's</normalizedToken>
material (the basis for the illustration) as 
<typeStatus>
<typeStatus>typotype</typeStatus>
</typeStatus>
.
</paragraph>
